---
/**
 * PipelineComparison
 *
 * Tabbed, side-by-side view of the two ingestion pipelines and what each
 * costs. The segmented control is CSS-only (no client JavaScript); each panel
 * holds a canvas flow diagram (rendered by scripts/diagrams/pipeline.ts) plus
 * its billing. Themes through the semantic colour tokens.
 *
 * Self-contained: takes no props. The content is specific to this article.
 */
---

<figure
  class="not-prose pipeline"
  aria-label="One-shot versus agentic ingestion, and the cost of each"
>
  <input
    class="pipeline__radio"
    type="radio"
    name="pipeline-variant"
    id="pipeline-oneshot"
    checked
  />
  <input
    class="pipeline__radio"
    type="radio"
    name="pipeline-variant"
    id="pipeline-agentic"
  />

  <div class="pipeline__tabs" role="presentation">
    <label class="pipeline__tab" for="pipeline-oneshot">One-shot</label>
    <label class="pipeline__tab" for="pipeline-agentic">Agentic</label>
  </div>

  <div class="pipeline__panel pipeline__panel--oneshot">
    <canvas
      class="pipeline__canvas"
      data-diagram="pipeline-oneshot"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Extract fans out to one triage task per candidate, which converge on a single relate task before the graph. Each stage is a single call."
    ></canvas>
    <p class="pipeline__note">
      Triage still fans out to one task per candidate – but each stage is a
      single call, so the bill stays close to the number of candidates.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="pipeline__panel pipeline__panel--agentic">
    <canvas
      class="pipeline__canvas"
      data-diagram="pipeline-agentic"
      role="img"
      aria-label="The same fan-out: extract to one triage thread per candidate, converging on a single relate thread before the graph. Each triage and relate thread is a loop of up to 25 turns, then a verifier of up to 2 tries."
    ></canvas>
    <p class="pipeline__note">
      The same fan-out – but each triage and relate unit is a durable thread: a
      loop of up to 25 turns, then a verifier (up to 2 tries). That is where the
      order-of-magnitude more inference goes.
    </p>
  </div>

  <figcaption class="pipeline__caption">
    Ingestion, one-shot versus agentic – and what each costs.
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<script src="../../scripts/diagrams/pipeline.ts"></script>

<style>
  .pipeline {
    position: relative;
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
    border: var(--border-hairline) solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: var(--space-1);
  }

  /* Radios drive the tabs; kept focusable, removed from layout. */
  .pipeline__radio {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .pipeline__tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: var(--border-hairline) solid var(--rule);
  }

  .pipeline__tab {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-2) var(--space-1);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: var(--border-thin) solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: calc(-1 * var(--border-hairline));
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .pipeline__tab:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  #pipeline-oneshot:checked
    ~ .pipeline__tabs
    .pipeline__tab[for="pipeline-oneshot"],
  #pipeline-agentic:checked
    ~ .pipeline__tabs
    .pipeline__tab[for="pipeline-agentic"] {
    color: var(--emphasis);
    border-bottom-color: var(--fg);
  }

  #pipeline-oneshot:focus-visible
    ~ .pipeline__tabs
    .pipeline__tab[for="pipeline-oneshot"],
  #pipeline-agentic:focus-visible
    ~ .pipeline__tabs
    .pipeline__tab[for="pipeline-agentic"] {
    outline: var(--outline-width) solid var(--highlight);
    outline-offset: var(--outline-offset-tight);
  }

  .pipeline__panel {
    display: none;
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }

  #pipeline-oneshot:checked ~ .pipeline__panel--oneshot,
  #pipeline-agentic:checked ~ .pipeline__panel--agentic {
    display: block;
  }

  .pipeline__canvas {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 800 / 240;
  }

  .pipeline__note {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-24);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .pipeline__caption {
    padding: 0 var(--space-4) var(--space-4);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-24);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .pipeline__tab {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
